About this area

Puerto Morelos

Located in Puerto Morelos, this vacation home is in the city center and near the beach. Moon Palace Golf Club and Puerto Morelos Reef are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those looking for area attractions can visit Arrecife de Puerto Morelos National Park and West Coast of Isla Mujeres, Punta Cancun, and Punta Nizuc National Park. Xoximilco and Selvatica Adventure Kingdom are also worth visiting.

Entire place

Whole house available for you to enjoy and relax your stay @ mayan Riviera. Perfect for families. Clean, quiet and Safe. 2 satellite WI-FI connections available for your convenience. For entertainment or work/school.
Has all those basic little things in the kitchen if you feel like prep a meal or convenient location with several options for take out. the complex has its own security guards 24/7
